Cell.Text: What happened?
S|Companions... th-they came sneaky, assault the fort. They released those beasts into the cages... Please brother... avenge our shed blood.... ohhh
And what about you?
[S] S|I'll be fine... I have a healing potion... You must hurry inside to help our brothers...
It's done...
Yes, we did it, we won the battle... But we lost our Leader, Krev. May his soul rest in peace in Sovngarde.
Any idea did they decide to attack us?

We were waiting to be attacked in retaliation to Farkas and Njada's death. But they attacked sooner than we expected. | Anyway, we had an important victory tonight. Krev must be proud of all of us now. Listen, Fjol needs to be notified of what happened. | Since he was the second in charge, he must claim our leadership now.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M60SE_Topic02: Any idea did they decide to attack us?

Cell.Text: I'll notify him!
[S] Good! We will be taking care of things here. We must clean up this mess, rebuild our defenses, and make the proper funerals. | Fjol will tell us the next steps.
Fjol!
Come on in. What brings you here?
The companions have just attacked Gallows Rock. But we defeated them...
By the nine! Did we have many casualties?

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M60FP_Topic02: The companions have just attacked Gallows Rock. But we defeated them...

Cell.Text: Yes... many brothers have fallen, including our leader Krev...

No... Krev... My best friend... but... He must be better than us now, for sure! | He must be drinking the most delicious mead, with the most delightful woman in Sovngarde. | And about the Companions... How many of them were werewolves?

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M60FP_Topic03: Yes… many brothers have fallen, including our leader Krev...

Cell.Text: Three, including Aela and Skjor!
Even though many of us have perished, this was a great victory for sure. | You know... I must tell you some things...
What things?

[S] A long time ago... Krev and I were Companions too. We were almost like twin brothers, we were inseparable in the battles. | But one day... We both were invited to ascend to the circle. | Fortunately, Krev noticed what the circle was about, and we fled before being forced to drink the cursed wolf's blood. | Since then, we have been fighting for the Silver Hand. They didn't know but Krev's mother was murdered by a werewolf... | We have been hiring valiant warriors who hate werewolves and Daedra more than anything. | Now, the Silver Hand had grown stronger than ever. But enough talk. We must inform the brothers about what happened.
And as a reward for the bravery and efforts annihilating wolves, I offer you the leadership of the Gallows Rock fort. Do you accept?
Yes, I accept!
[S] Now you are officially a Stronghold Chief, and the second on the succession line of our group. Congratulations! Please, accept these gifts.
